{"type": "article", "id": 21697, "title": "“hand touch” by Edyta Cieloch", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161349TUAC4IFodbn8cyRB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组白色的瓷器餐具有着漂亮的蓝色圆晕。餐具的中心有蓝色的圆环，圆环之外有几层浅色的圆环，一圈圈散开，由深至浅，就像水中的波纹。餐具的外侧也有类似的波纹，是从下至上由深变浅的，非常素雅。设计者是波兰的陶瓷设计师 Edyta Cieloch，她先在瓷器上涂钴类颜料，然后上釉焙烧。这里是他们的工作室链接。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161346UqXRtyk5pjaw0SOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.59779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161347UbdVsoONWMeEiq1L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161347dZHlAm2zNViwu5vt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161348Yx2cCTuG1XMt8fSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}